name: Ccie Rack Rentals
short_description:
Our offerings include racks for the Routing and Switching, Security, and Service Provider study fields in addition to workbooks and virtual mock lab exams for Routing and Switching.

Presidential Data has dedicated itself to offering a superior Cisco training experience. We offer clear advantages for using our training solutions, including our use of the most current and comprehensive Cisco equipment for our CCIE Rack Rentals and delivering some of the lowest rates in the market. Our Mock-up Lab Exams as well as our CCIE Rack Rental options match the official blueprints you'll encounter during the actual CCIE Lab Exam.
